name: Perl Look Bracelet
description:
Chunky, fancier and a little special.

These bracelets will be much thicker and higher quality than my other elasticated bracelets as they will use 10mm beads with a Perl Look finish to give the jewelry a much more elegant style. 

Currently, the colours I have ordered are Blue, a random mix and a Christmas Mix. These will be made and ready for sale when people show enough interest for me to buy more stock.

f you have any further questions, please feel free to ask.

name: Christmas Collection!
description:
It's never too early to start stocking up on Christmas presents and this adorable charm bracelet is perfect for friends, family or even a little gift for yourself!

This bracelet comes in either Traditional Christmas colours, Red & Green or a Frosty mix of Blue and White, with a random Christmas charm attached to make it that much cuter!
 
All bracelets are handmade and size between 7 - 8 inches and  ~~ only shipped within the UK ~~

These are made as and when I receive an order, and will be made specially for you!

name: Rainbow! Coloured Bracelet with Charm.
description:
This small and cute little elasticated bracelet is made in 6 different colours; Red, Orange, Yellow, Green, Blue, and Purple. All come with a sweet but random silver metal charm. (If you have a request for a certain charm please contact me and I will do my best!)

All bracelets are handmade and size between 7 - 8 inches and  ~~ only shipped within the UK ~~

These are made as and when I receive an order, and will be made specially for you!

name: Vineyard! Mixed bead elasticated bracelet.
description:
Beautiful elasticated beaded bracelet with a mix of glass and acrylic beads of varied shapes and sizes. All Bracelets range in size from 7 inch to 7 and a half inches around. Please ensure they will fit and keep in mind they will stretch.

Themed "Vineyard" as beads are a mix of green and purple colours. Charms will include small leaf and raindrop shape beads as well as larger "Indian style" ones.
Every bracelet I make will be 100% unique and vary in beads therefore there is only 1 of each design available, so buy quick! (All will be of equal value)

All bracelets are handmade and size between 7 - 8 inches and  ~~ only shipped within the UK ~~

These are made as and when I receive an order, and will be made specially for you!
